sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant React as React Frontend
    participant Main as Main Server
    participant DB as Main SQLite
    participant Strat as WorkerSelectionStrategy
    participant Worker as Chosen Worker
    participant SplitDB as Worker Split-DB

    React->>Main: POST /API/V1/Company (CompanyName, Slug, ...)
    Main->>Main: Validate session + payload
    Main->>DB: SELECT eligible WorkerNode rows
    DB-->>Main: candidates
    Main->>Strat: pick(candidates, strategyCode)
    Strat-->>Main: WorkerNode (id=3)
    Main->>DB: INSERT Company (minimal identity, WorkerNodeId=3)
    Main->>DB: INSERT WorkerSelectionEvent
    Main->>Worker: POST /Internal/Company (full payload, X-Correlation-Id)
    Worker->>SplitDB: Create RootCompany + AppCompanyShard
    SplitDB-->>Worker: ok
    Worker-->>Main: 201 Created (CompanyId)
    Main-->>React: 201 Created (CompanyId, CompanySlug)

    Note over Main,Worker: Failure path: if Worker returns 5xx,<br/>Main retries (max 3, exp backoff)<br/>then surfaces WorkerUnreachable per 08-error-contract.md
